# strict reverse-path filter, IPv4-scoped: drop when the reverse route is
# missing (oif 0). The shipped code was doubly broken: `ip fib` is a syntax
# error (never loaded) and `!= 0` was inverted (dropped legit traffic).
+ iifname "eth0" meta nfproto ipv4 fib saddr . iif oif 0 counter drop
+ iifname "eth1" meta nfproto ipv4 fib saddr . iif oif 0 counter drop
- ip fib
- oif != 0
